text:
This is a seriously good piece of banana cake. Taste and texture is seriously on point. Oh my. To me, this is the perfect banana cake. Wow üëçperfection. Totally worth it. Glad I got it... had a sense it was good from the looks of it at their shop even tho I just had lunch.

I tried without heating up and the texture is soft and on point. I would recommend without heating up so that it's soft? Will try heated up next time just to compare.
I hope gomgom stays like this foreverü•π I order it for lunch everyday. The sandwich are fresh and clean. Portions are suitable and always follow delivery instructions. Nothing special but a must.
Bagus best banana cake. No joke better than my mother's. Authentic and fragrant. Really best I had

I remember it being pretty good but dayum did the standards drop to the ground. The amount of meat is quite little, the bread is so dry for some reason. I don't think I'll wanna visit this place again after this time around
Nice awesomely bake banana bread cake. Moist , fluffy  n compact n soft texture. Best personal  consume option with steaming or cold from fridge. Worth the money for big loaf.
